      News story
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Foreign Secretary visits Japan, teaches English to Japanese school children
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  
  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    The Foreign Secretary, Jeremy Hunt will fly the flag for Britain today (Monday 15 April) as he visits a Japanese high school to teach English and share with students why it is the ‘language of opportunity’.
 
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="column-two-thirds metadata-column">
